p on the 1960s as well as to the history of Christianity in the western world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh1 aAbrams, Lynn, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAllitt, Patrick, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCaulier, Brigitte, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCazorla-Sanchez, Antonio, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChristie, Nancy, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aF.Browne, Sarah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFetner, Tina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aG.Brown, Callum, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGauvreau, Michael, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aGauvreau, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHarris, Alana, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeath, Melanie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeathorn, Stephen J., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aHeathorn, Stephen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLaing, Heather, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcLeod, Hugh, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aN.Flatt, Kevin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPasture, Patrick, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVan Rahden, Till, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWoodcock Tentler, Leslie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/rela